articles.author: Barbara Erling
articles.title: Flood-hit central Europe will get billions in EU aid, von der Leyen promises - Reuters
articles.description: The European Union will make billions of euros available to help central Europe recover from severe floods, European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen said on Thursday, as she pledged support for regions that have been devastated by the deluge.
